                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mb-4">
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="img-box">
                        <img src="images/program-3.jpg" alt="Flexibility & Yoga">
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-box">
                        <h5>
                            FLEXIBILITY & YOGA
                        </h5>
                        <p>
                            Increase mobility, reduce stress, and improve balance with our flexibility and yoga training program.
                        </p>
